{"tid":2229134,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁振英斥楊潤雄當習總言論耳邊風 誣蔑教協為「陀地工會」","createTime":"2020-10-04T07:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T00:54:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"21994ea896e6ecbd2f0e2eb74b4fa86bedec95bc","tid":2229134,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英牽頭成立的「803基金」，日前入稟高等法院申請司法覆核，要求高院下令教育局局長楊潤雄交代被投訴的教師身份和資料後，梁振英今天再在網誌撰文，不點名批評楊潤雄將中共國家主席習近平名句「為官避事平生恥」當耳邊風，又將教協比喻為「佗（陀）地工會」，施壓警告「教協不倒大亂不止」。<br />\n<br />\n連日頻頻發文，要求教育局公開被裁定專業操守失當的教師及學校名稱等資料的梁振英，批鬥行動周日無休，今天於社交媒體發文，將教師與教協比喻為雙手紋青龍白虎的司機及「佗（陀）地」，暗示為「交通督導員」的教育局不想惹事，為官避事。梁其後又引用習近平「為官避事平生恥」的言論，不點名批評教育局局長楊潤雄「當耳邊風」，指教育局態度依舊「按既有機制和程序辦事」，心態是等到法官有判決後，「如果上法庭，法官判我要做，我就做，沒有人可以埋怨我」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/JU2YDJ7XRNDVBFVA2TFNJ6D65Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FJU2YDJ7XRNDVBFVA2TFNJ6D65Q%2F&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=f3966c48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FJU2YDJ7XRNDVBFVA2TFNJ6D65Q%2F&h=bee3ce21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/JU2YDJ7XRNDVBFVA2TFNJ6D65Q/</a>"},{"pid":"d6454cefa756ab3e403179392984ddc212ac25e7","tid":2229134,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa79c3ff6758abaaccd2cd068ba51d0c5e284bde","tid":2229134,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6454cefa756ab3e403179392984ddc212ac25e7","tid":2229134,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\